ctified the believer thrice\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40406,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/06\/greatest-losers-rich\/","url_meta":{"origin":14288,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Greatest losers are super rich unless charitable","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: I arrived at the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, who was sitting in the shade of the Ka\u2019bah and saying, \u201cThey have the greatest loss, by the Lord of the Ka\u2019bah, they have the greatest loss, by the Lord of the Ka\u2019bah.\u201d I said, \u201cWho\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23730,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/15\/tawaf-every-step-reward\/","url_meta":{"origin":14288,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawaf: Every step around the Ka\u2019bah is rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever circles the Ka\u2019bah seven times and prays two cycles\u00a0will be rewarded as if he had freed a slave. A man does not raise his foot, nor bring it back down, but that ten good\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21726,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/23\/life-believers-sacred-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":14288,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sanctity: Life of believers more sacred than the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 23, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe passing of the world is less significant to Allah than the killing of a believer without a just cause.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2619 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0632\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9855,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/16\/prophet-khutbah-hajjat-al-wadaa\/","url_meta":{"origin":14288,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Arafat: The Prophet&#8217;s farewell sermon at Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said during his farewell sermon, \u201cWhich month do you know has the greatest sanctity?\u201d They said, \u201cNo doubt, this month of ours, Dhul Hijjah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhich city do you know has the greatest sanctity?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context